original: Dahlberg, Ernst Åke Juilius, komminister, Forshem, f. 11/3/08 i Skövde av Ernst o. Gerda Dahliberg. G. 36 m. Inga Börjeson. Barn: Catharina f. 38, d. 41, Per 39, Olov 42, Lars 44. — Stiid:ex. i Gbg 27, teol. fil. ex. 28, teol. kand. o. prästv. f. Skara stift 33. Tjg. s. past:adj. o. kyrkoadj. i Lyrestad, v. kommin. i Skara samt past:-adj. o. v. pastor i Flo, kommin. i Fors-hem sed. 39. Tjänstled. 44-46 f. tjänst i Sv. kyrkans diakonistyr. (andre iingd:sekr. o. red. f. Vår Kyrka).
translated: Dahlberg, Ernst Åke Juilius, vicar, Forshem, born March 11, 1908 in Skövde to Ernst and Gerda Dahliberg. Married in 1936 to Inga Börjeson. Children: Catharina born in 1938, died in 1941, Per born in 1939, Olov born in 1942, and Lars born in 1944. Education: Studentexamen in Gothenburg in 1927, fil. kand. in theology in 1928, theological candidate and ordained minister in Skara diocese in 1933. Employed as assistant vicar and curate in Lyrestad, vicar in Skara, assistant vicar and vicar in Flo, and vicar in Forshem since 1939. On leave from 1944-1946 to serve in the Swedish Church's diaconal service. Also served as secretary and editor for "Our Church".
